    "Table 7, shows a summary of all the studies that have used hybrid DL techniques.",
    "The analysis of categorical variable transformation techniques and their compatibility with DL models are the main objectives of this study Hien et al (2020).",
    "To predict student academic performance, this study compared the effectiveness of label encoding, one-hot encoding, and \"learned\" embedding encoding with deep learning methods, such as DNNs and LSTM.",
    "The findings of the experiment demonstrated that the \"learned\" embedding encoding method for categorical data transformation enhanced deep learning model's performance, and that its application in conjunction with LSTM produced excellent results.",
